<h2>Connection Tutorial for the Mac</h2>
- Download<a href="http://www.solidsun.com/cm/"> Cantrip</a>, a free mudclient.<br />
- Go to File > New > New World (apple + N)<br />
- Push the connection button.<br />
- Put in the address and port information in the address box that comes up. (Address: xaos-mud.org | Port: 5000)<br />
- Connect to xaos.<br />
Follow the instructions continuing from the "<a href="index.php?page=newbies">Becoming a Xaos Player"</a> section.
